Title: Into the Vale
Description:
Ah, I have been waiting for your arrival, traveler.

I wish we could meet in better times, but alas, I fear the situation in the Vale is quite dire.

But let us not speak of that now. Go visit Matron Vi Vinh at the Shrine of Seven Stars.

She should be able to settle you in.
ObjectivesText: Speak to Matron Vi Vinh at the Shrine of Seven Stars in the Vale of Eternal Blossoms.
